hat day and better that goal.', 63991, 0), (404383, 'It doesn''t matter what anybody thinks of what I do. The clock doesn''t lie.', 63991, 0), (404384, 'You can have your titular recognition. I''ll take money and power.', 2277, 0), (404385, 'Normal is not something to aspire to  it''s something to get away from.', 63992, 0), (404386, 'I''m always making a comeback but nobody ever tells me where I''ve been.', 9623, 0), (404387, 'My passions were all gathered together like fingers that made a fist. Drive is considered aggression today  I knew it then as purpose.', 13058, 0), (404388, 'In the multitude of middle-aged men who go about their vocations in a daily course determined for them much in the same way as they tie their cravats  there is always a good number who once meant to shape their own deeds and alter the world a little.', 215, 0), (404389, 'Remember if people talk behind your back  it only means you''re two steps ahead!', 156, 0), (404390, 'It''s a sign of your own worth sometimes if you are hated by the right people.', 15716, 0), (404391, 'For me it''s the challenge-the challenge to try to beat myself or do better than I did in the past. I try to keep in mind not what I have accomplished but what I have to try to accomplish in the future.', 63993, 0), (404392, 'There''s a very fine line between a groove and a rut  a fine line between eccentrics and people who are just plain nuts.', 63994, 0), (404393, 'Promises that you make to yourself are often like the Japanese plum tree-they bear no fruit.', 63995, 0), (404394, 'I am not sending messages with my feet. All I ever wanted was not to come up empty. I did it for the dough  and the old applause.', 62652, 0), (404395, 'First say to yourself what you would be  and then do what you have to do.', 1328, 0), (404396, 'I can honestly say that I was never affected by the question of the success of an undertaking. If I felt it was the right thing to do  I was for it regardless of the possible outcome.', 12971, 0), (404397, 'What exactly is success? For me it is to be found not in applause  but in the satisfaction of feeling that one is realizing one''s ideal.', 5934, 0), (404398, 'We can do whatever we wish to do provided our wish is strong enough. ... What do you want most to do? That''s what I have to keep asking myself  in the face of difficulties.', 3172, 0), (404399, 'To be what we are  and to become what we are capable of becoming  is the only end of life.', 2478, 0), (404400, 'You have to define success in your own way. What maintains your dignity and integrity and what is your life''s plan  where do you want to put your efforts. I could be richer and more famous  but I would have to give up things that are of infinitely more value.', 63942, 0);
